  "keyFeatures": [
    "One-command installation of complete agentic coding setup",
    "11 specialized agents for code review, testing, security, and implementation",
    "22 skills for feature development, bug fixing, refactoring, and releases",
    "18 rules covering code standards, API design, testing, and security",
    "25 commands for board management, planning, quality audits, and workflows",
    "Multi-tool support with adapters for Cursor, GitHub Copilot, Claude Code, OpenCode, Windsurf, Amp, Codex, Gemini, and Cline",
    "Built-in MCP integrations for GitHub, Context7, Filesystem, Playwright, and Brave Search",
    "Sub-agentic architecture with parallel delegation and dependency-aware orchestration",
    "GitHub Projects V2 board management with automated issue creation and status tracking",
    "Spec-driven development with modular documentation structure"
  ],
